Customers typically see visible results in as little as 1 to 2 treatments, but everyones starting point is different, so results will vary depending upon usage. Active Wow is gentle and natural enough to be used twice per day for consecutive days until your desired whitening is achieved. You can also use it on occasion to keep your teeth white after youve achieved your desired level.

Teeth Whitening Redefined - Simple, Natural Ingredients

Active Wow - Activated Coconut Powder The natural way to whitening your teeth

Derived from the highest-quality coconut sources, Active Wows activated charcoal formula is safe to use for whitening your teeth, while being easy on your gums. Active Wow naturally whitens your teeth, not through harsh dental-grade whitening peroxides, but through the power of Activated Charcoal, natures best purifies and detoxifiers.

Active Wows unique formula whitens your teeth over time, and helps remove stains from a number of causes: coffee-stains, wine, cigarettes, and more - all without harsh chemicals or bleach.

  • Naturally Derived
  • Made in the USA

  • Hassle Free, brush like normal
  • Purifies and Detoxifies

Active Wow Uses Naturally Derived Whitening Ingredients

Organic Coconut Activated Charcoal Powder

Activated charcoal works by pulling stains off your teeth through a process 'adsorption'. Coconut is the purest form of food-grade charcoal.

Bentonite

Bentonite is great for the remineralizing your teeth due to its high mineral content. It also absorbs toxins naturally, and is easy on your gums.

Orange Seed Oil

A natural teeth whitener, orange seed oil helps smooth your teeth whitening experience. It has numerous anti-inflammatory and antiseptic qualities, making it the perfect addition to Active Wows all natural whitening formula.

Read more
View larger

Easy-to-Follow Instructions For Active Wow Teeth Whitening

- Make toothbrush slightly wet.

- Remove excess water from brush.

- Dip brush into the charcoal powder.

- Dab off excess powder (a little goes a long way).

- Brush teeth like normal, for 1-2 minutes.

- Rinse mouth thoroughly to remove the charcoal. Spit directly into the sink and use water to keep the sink clean.

PJ
5.0 out of 5 stars Trust Your Fellow Reviewers!
May 10, 2017
Color: As shown in the image | Verified Purchase
This stuff works really well! I noticed whiter teeth after the first use. I've convinced friends with yellower teeth than mine to try and the results are dramatic! I use it a few times a week and think it works really well!

As others have said, this stuff is a MESS. Tips I've found after several uses are:
-Use it in the shower. You can rinse the shower when you're done.
-Make sure you brush with your mouth closed the entire time. It seems obvious but makes a difference.
-Designate a toothbrush to this stuff. It will turn your brush black, no matter how many times you rinse.
-Focus on the front teeth and don't worry about your molars like you would with normal paste. No one cares if your molars are white.
-Spit into the sink THEN turn on the water. If you spit with the water running, it'll spray black everywhere.
-After you spit the first time, keep brushing. I usually brush until I spit clear.
-Brush gently. My friend brushed too hard and got charcoal in her gums them had a bum-looking tooth all day.
-Floss afterwards or use mouthwash. It'll help get all the tiny particles between your teeth out.

The before and after picture are after ONE time using it.
